@startuml 10 Gateway Types - Enterprise AI Architecture
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title Enterprise AI Gateway Architecture\n10 Specialized Gateway Types\n(Healthcare Insurance Multi-Agent Platform)

package "Request Flow" {
  actor "Provider" as Provider
  actor "Clinical Reviewer" as Reviewer
  
  Provider --> G1
  Reviewer --> G1
}

rectangle "**1. AI GATEWAY**\n(Application Layer)" as G1 #E3F2FD {
  rectangle "Multi-LLM Router" as Router {
    ' Simple Query → Llama 3 ($0.02)
    ' Standard → GPT-4o-mini ($0.05)
    ' Complex → GPT-4o ($0.30)
    ' Code → Claude 3.5 ($0.25)
  }
  rectangle "Load Balancer" as LB {
    ' GPT-4o Instance 1
    ' GPT-4o Instance 2
    ' GPT-4o Instance 3
  }
  rectangle "Cost Optimizer" as Cost {
    ' Token tracking
    ' Budget enforcement
    ' Usage analytics
  }
  rectangle "Failover Handler" as Failover {
    ' Primary: GPT-4o
    ' Backup: Claude 3.5
    ' Emergency: GPT-3.5
  }
}

note right of G1
  **Purpose:** Multi-model orchestration
  **Technologies:** Portkey, LiteLLM, OpenRouter
  
  **Routing Logic:**
  • Query complexity score
  • Cost per token
  • Latency requirements
  • Model availability
  
  **Cost Savings:**
  • Before: $150/day (all GPT-4o)
  • After: $45/day (smart routing)
  • Savings: 70%
  
  **Metrics:**
  • Requests/sec: 500
  • P95 latency: 2.1s
  • Error rate: 0.3%
end note

rectangle "**2. SECURITY GATEWAY (LLM Firewall)**\n(Security Layer)" as G2 #FFEBEE {
  rectangle "Input Scanner" as InputScan {
    ' Prompt injection detection
    ' Jailbreak prevention
    ' PII/PHI detection
    ' Toxicity filtering
  }
  rectangle "Threat Detector" as Threat {
    ' SQL injection
    ' XSS attempts
    ' LDAP injection
    ' Command injection
  }
  rectangle "Data Masker" as Mask {
    ' SSN redaction
    ' PHI anonymization
    ' Credit card masking
  }
  rectangle "Output Scanner" as OutputScan {
    ' PHI leakage prevention
    ' Toxic content filter
    ' Hallucination detection
    ' Compliance check
  }
}

note right of G2
  **Purpose:** AI-specific threat protection
  **Technologies:** Lakera AI, Protect AI,
                    NVIDIA NeMo Guardrails
  
  **Blocked Threats (Last 30 Days):**
  • Prompt injections: 234
  • Jailbreak attempts: 67
  • PHI exposure: 12
  • Toxic outputs: 89
  
  **Detection Accuracy:**
  • Prompt injection: 98.5%
  • PII detection: 99.2%
  • Toxicity: 97.8%
  
  **Latency Impact:** +50ms
end note

rectangle "**3. AGENT GATEWAY**\n(Agent Orchestration Layer)" as G3 #E8F5E9 {
  rectangle "Agent Registry" as AgentReg {
    json registry {
      "clinical-agent": {
        "replicas": 10,
        "status": "healthy",
        "version": "v2.3.1"
      }
    }
  }
  rectangle "Agent Router" as AgentRouter {
    ' Capability-based routing
    ' Load balancing
    ' Health checks
  }
  rectangle "A2A Protocol Handler" as A2A {
    ' Message validation
    ' Schema enforcement
    ' Observability
  }
  rectangle "Agent Mesh" as Mesh {
    ' Service discovery
    ' Circuit breaker
    ' Retry logic
  }
}

note right of G3
  **Purpose:** Agent-to-agent communication
  **Technologies:** Kong, Dapr, Istio
  
  **Agent Discovery:**
  1. Query: "Which agent handles benefits?"
  2. Registry lookup
  3. Return: benefits-agent replicas
  4. Load balance across 5 replicas
  
  **Health Monitoring:**
  • Heartbeat: 10s interval
  • Unhealthy threshold: 3 failures
  • Auto-scaling: CPU > 70%
  
  **A2A Messages/Day:** 500K
  **Latency P95:** 45ms
end note

rectangle "**4. MCP GATEWAY**\n(Tool Layer)" as G4 #FFF3E0 {
  rectangle "Tool Registry" as ToolReg {
    json tools {
      "mcg_guidelines": {
        "auth": "OAuth2",
        "permissions": "[clinical-agent]",
        "rate_limit": "100/min"
      }
    }
  }
  rectangle "Tool Router" as ToolRouter {
    ' Capability matching
    ' Permission check
    ' Authentication
  }
  rectangle "Schema Validator" as Schema {
    ' Parameter validation
    ' Type checking
    ' Version compatibility
  }
  rectangle "Tool Auditor" as ToolAudit {
    ' Usage logging
    ' Cost tracking
    ' Compliance audit
  }
}

note right of G4
  **Purpose:** MCP tool discovery & governance
  **Technologies:** MCP servers, Vault
  
  **Tool Discovery Flow:**
  1. Agent: "I need MCG guidelines"
  2. Query registry by capability
  3. Check permissions (RBAC)
  4. Retrieve OAuth token
  5. Validate request schema
  6. Execute tool call
  7. Audit log
  
  **Registered Tools:** 47
  **Tool Calls/Day:** 250K
  **Auth Success Rate:** 99.8%
end note

rectangle "**5. LLM GATEWAY**\n(Model Layer)" as G5 #FCE4EC {
  rectangle "Task Classifier" as Classifier {
    ' Clinical reasoning
    ' Document extraction
    ' Simple Q&A
  }
  rectangle "Model Selector" as Selector {
    ' Clinical → GPT-4o
    ' Extraction → GPT-4o-mini
    ' Q&A → GPT-3.5
  }
  rectangle "Cache Layer" as CacheLLM {
    ' Semantic caching
    ' 1-hour TTL
    ' Cache hit: 35%
  }
  rectangle "Retry Handler" as Retry {
    ' Exponential backoff
    ' Max retries: 3
    ' Timeout: 30s
  }
}

note right of G5
  **Purpose:** LLM request optimization
  **Technologies:** LiteLLM, Portkey, Helicone
  
  **Task-Based Routing:**
  • Clinical review → GPT-4o (96% accuracy)
  • Entity extraction → GPT-4o-mini (94% accuracy)
  • FAQ → GPT-3.5 (88% accuracy)
  
  **Performance:**
  • Cache hit rate: 35%
  • Cache savings: $800/day
  • Latency reduction: 85%
  
  **Fallback Chain:**
  GPT-4o → Claude 3.5 → GPT-3.5
end note

rectangle "**6. HUMAN APPROVAL GATEWAY**\n(HITL Layer)" as G6 #F3E5F5 {
  rectangle "Risk Assessor" as Risk {
    ' Amount-based
    ' Complexity-based
    ' Confidence-based
  }
  rectangle "Workflow Engine" as Workflow {
    ' Route to queue
    ' Assign reviewer
    ' SLA tracking
  }
  rectangle "Escalation Manager" as Escalate {
    ' Low → Auto-approve
    ' Medium → Supervisor
    ' High → Senior reviewer
    ' Critical → Board
  }
  rectangle "Override Tracker" as Override {
    ' AI vs Human decision
    ' Reason capture
    ' Pattern analysis
  }
}

note right of G6
  **Purpose:** Mandatory human oversight
  **Technologies:** ServiceNow, Custom
  
  **Risk-Based Routing:**
  | Risk | Action |
  |------|--------|
  | <0.4 | Auto-execute |
  | 0.4-0.75 | Supervisor |
  | 0.75-0.9 | Senior approval |
  | >0.9 | Board review |
  
  **HITL Metrics:**
  • Auto-approval: 72%
  • Human review: 28%
  • Override rate: 8%
  • Avg review time: 15 min
end note

rectangle "**7. DATA GATEWAY**\n(Data Security Layer)" as G7 #E0F2F1 {
  rectangle "Access Controller" as Access {
    ' Row-level security
    ' Column masking
    ' RBAC enforcement
  }
  rectangle "Query Optimizer" as QueryOpt {
    ' Query rewriting
    ' Index hints
    ' Connection pooling
  }
  rectangle "Audit Logger" as DataAudit {
    ' All queries logged
    ' Data lineage
    ' PHI access tracking
  }
  rectangle "Injection Preventer" as Injection {
    ' SQL validation
    ' Parameterized queries
    ' Whitelist enforcement
  }
}

note right of G7
  **Purpose:** Secure data access
  **Technologies:** OPA, Database proxies
  
  **Row-Level Security Example:**
  ```sql
  -- Agent query
  SELECT * FROM patients WHERE id = 123456
  
  -- Gateway transforms to
  SELECT * FROM patients 
  WHERE id = 123456 
  AND organization_id = <agent_org_id>
  ```
  
  **Column Masking:**
  • SSN → ***-**-1234
  • DOB → 19XX-XX-XX
  • Name → J*** S***
  
  **Audit:** 100% queries logged
end note

rectangle "**8. VECTOR GATEWAY**\n(RAG Layer)" as G8 #FFF9C4 {
  rectangle "Query Router" as VectorRouter {
    ' Clinical → Milvus Clinical
    ' Policy → Milvus Policy
    ' Multi-collection search
  }
  rectangle "Metadata Filter" as Filter {
    ' Document type
    ' Date range
    ' Organization
  }
  rectangle "Hybrid Retriever" as Hybrid {
    ' Vector search (cosine)
    ' BM25 keyword
    ' Fusion ranking
  }
  rectangle "Reranker" as Reranker {
    ' Cross-encoder
    ' Diversity filter
    ' Top-K selection
  }
}

note right of G8
  **Purpose:** Vector DB access control
  **Technologies:** Milvus, Pinecone
  
  **Hybrid Retrieval:**
  1. BM25 search → Top 100
  2. Vector search → Top 100
  3. Metadata filter
  4. Cross-encoder rerank
  5. Return Top 10
  
  **Collections:**
  • clinical_guidelines: 5M vectors
  • policy_documents: 2M vectors
  • case_history: 10M vectors
  
  **Performance:**
  • P95 latency: 120ms
  • Relevance@10: 0.89
end note

rectangle "**9. WORKFLOW GATEWAY**\n(Orchestration Layer)" as G9 #E1F5FE {
  rectangle "State Manager" as State {
    ' Workflow state persistence
    ' Checkpoint creation
    ' State recovery
  }
  rectangle "Saga Coordinator" as Saga {
    ' Distributed transactions
    ' Compensation logic
    ' Rollback handling
  }
  rectangle "Retry Manager" as RetryWF {
    ' Failed step retry
    ' Exponential backoff
    ' Dead letter queue
  }
  rectangle "SLA Monitor" as SLAMon {
    ' Workflow timing
    ' SLA violation alerts
    ' Auto-escalation
  }
}

note right of G9
  **Purpose:** Workflow orchestration
  **Technologies:** Temporal, Camunda
  
  **PA Workflow Steps:**
  1. Intake (2 min)
  2. Eligibility (15 sec)
  3. Benefits (20 sec)
  4. Clinical review (5 min)
  5. Decision (10 sec)
  6. Notification (30 sec)
  
  **Total:** ~8 minutes
  
  **Reliability:**
  • Success rate: 99.2%
  • Auto-retry: 95% success
  • Manual intervention: 0.8%
end note

rectangle "**10. OBSERVABILITY GATEWAY**\n(Monitoring Layer)" as G10 #ECEFF1 {
  rectangle "Trace Collector" as Trace {
    ' OpenTelemetry
    ' Distributed tracing
    ' Span correlation
  }
  rectangle "Metrics Aggregator" as Metrics {
    ' Prometheus
    ' Token usage
    ' Latency tracking
    ' Cost attribution
  }
  rectangle "Log Aggregator" as Logs {
    ' ELK Stack
    ' Structured logging
    ' Log correlation
  }
  rectangle "Cost Tracker" as CostTrack {
    ' Per-request cost
    ' Per-agent cost
    ' Total platform cost
  }
}

note right of G10
  **Purpose:** Comprehensive monitoring
  **Technologies:** OTel, LangSmith, Prometheus
  
  **Observability Pillars:**
  • Traces: Every request
  • Metrics: 200+ metrics
  • Logs: All events
  • Costs: Per-request tracking
  
  **Dashboards:**
  • AI Platform Overview
  • Agent Performance
  • Cost Analytics
  • Error Tracking
  
  **Alerts:** 45 alert rules
  **Retention:** 30 days (hot), 1 year (cold)
end note

' Gateway Flow
G1 --> G2 : LLM request
G2 --> G3 : Secure request
G3 --> G4 : Agent call
G4 --> G5 : Tool execution
G5 --> G6 : Decision review
G6 --> G7 : Data access
G7 --> G8 : RAG retrieval
G8 --> G9 : Workflow step
G9 --> G10 : Observability

note bottom
  **Gateway Architecture Benefits:**
  • Separation of concerns
  • Independent scaling
  • Specialized optimization
  • Clear responsibility
  • Enhanced security
  • Better observability
  
  **Total Latency Impact:** ~200ms
  **Security Coverage:** 99.8%
  **Cost Optimization:** 70% savings
end note

@enduml
